1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,115
Pause.

2
00:00:01,115 --> 00:00:06,363
Place one hand near your heart or
wherever feels comforting.

3
00:00:12,363 --> 00:00:12,363
<break time="3s" />

4
00:00:12,363 --> 00:00:15,335
Take a gentle breath.

5
00:00:15,335 --> 00:00:19,097
Now notice what is hard right now.

6
00:00:19,097 --> 00:00:21,605
You do not have to explain it.

7
00:00:21,605 --> 00:00:24,624
You do not have to fix it.

8
00:00:24,624 --> 00:00:27,318
Just name it quietly.

9
00:00:27,318 --> 00:00:29,268
This is hard.

10
00:00:29,268 --> 00:00:34,051
Now remind yourself: A part of me is
struggling.

11
00:00:34,051 --> 00:00:37,580
And that part deserves compassion.

12
00:00:37,580 --> 00:00:48,308
Silently say: I see you. I am here with
you. We can take this one step at a time.

13
00:00:54,308 --> 00:00:54,308
<break time="3s" />

14
00:00:54,308 --> 00:00:57,466
Take one more breath.

15
00:00:57,466 --> 00:01:01,599
Let the words land as much as they can.

16
00:01:01,599 --> 00:01:05,500
You do not need to feel perfect
compassion.

17
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:07,729
A small pause is enough.

